``` {.bash org-language="sh"}
sudo cryptsetup open /dev/sdb savolla
# it will ask for password
mkdir ./0
sudo mount /dev/mapper/savolla ./0
```

you also want to see [[Unmount Luks Encrypted Drive]] when you finish
